You hear life. Great. 你听到有生命，不错。

297
00:28:12,580 --> 00:28:14,870
We calculate. Calculations work. 我们计算过了，而计算的结果是

298
00:28:15,330 --> 00:28:16,870
We identified the drone model. 确定是个无人潜艇

299
