I don't understand, sir. I'm just asking to look. 我不明白，长官，我只是请求查看

303
00:28:34,680 --> 00:28:38,190
- I promised captain Grandchamp... - Bullshit promises. -我承诺格兰夏普船长了。 -狗屁承诺

