Here at CIRA, we hang our heads in shame. 我们在CIRA丢尽了脸面

307
00:28:52,280 --> 00:28:54,030
Once and for all, Chanteraide, 一次就够了，尚特莱

308
00:28:54,200 --> 00:28:55,620
this is the military. 这是军队

309
00:28:55,790 --> 00:28:57,000
Not art school. 不是艺术学院

310
00:28:59,620 --> 00:29:00,880
Morning, captain. 早上好，长官

311
00:29:01,170 --> 00:29:04,300
- What does he want? - It's the chopper, I guess. -他想要啥？ -我猜可能是直升机

312
