313
00:29:08,300 --> 00:29:09,590
Check flies. 检查下校门

314
00:29:10,340 --> 00:29:11,260
All clear. 没问题

315
00:29:13,100 --> 00:29:15,140
You heard the President's speech? 你听了总统的演说了吗？

316
00:29:21,440 --> 00:29:22,860
Morning, admiral. 早上好，上将。

317
00:29:23,110 --> 00:29:23,940
At ease. 稍息

318
00:29:29,610 --> 00:29:32,450
One lemon, two lemons, three lemons. 一个柠檬，两个柠檬，三个柠檬

319
