326
00:29:51,630 --> 00:29:52,890
A biggie. 厉害了

327
00:29:56,720 --> 00:29:57,970
Second lemon. 柠檬二号

328
00:29:59,980 --> 00:30:02,980
The President dispatches ground forces to Finland. 总统正式向芬兰派遣了地面部队

329
