330
00:30:09,150 --> 00:30:11,990
First time ever, all lines of communication down. 有史以来第一次，所有的通信线路都切断了

331
00:30:15,580 --> 00:30:16,700
Third lemon. 柠檬三号

332
00:30:19,370 --> 00:30:21,500
Presidential orders to reinforce our posture. 总统命令捍卫我们的立场

333
00:30:22,460 --> 00:30:23,420
In other words, 换句话说

334
00:30:23,540 --> 00:30:26,040
one nuclear ballistic sub in the water. 一艘核潜艇要出动了

335
