Fact is, you guys pulled off an act of incredible bravery. 事实上，你们表现得非常勇敢

339
00:30:46,440 --> 00:30:49,400
When I commanded <i>Titan</i>, I'd have done the same. 我指挥泰坦号的时候，也做过同样的事。

340
00:30:49,780 --> 00:30:50,610
So, 所以

341
00:30:51,240 --> 00:30:52,490
Grandchamp... 格兰夏普

342
00:30:53,900 --> 00:30:57,070
