358
00:31:53,010 --> 00:31:54,840
You have a problem with that? 有什么问题吗？

359
00:31:56,590 --> 00:31:58,430
- At your command, admiral. - Very good. -听你指挥，上将 -很好

360
00:31:58,590 --> 00:32:01,930
You'll escort Formidable until it goes stealth in blue water. 你负责护送无畏号，直到它消失在深海。

