415
00:36:44,670 --> 00:36:45,880
Sound signals. 声音信号

416
00:36:46,720 --> 00:36:47,720
Sounds. 还有声音

417
00:36:47,880 --> 00:36:49,220
You have perfect pitch? 你有绝对音感？

418
00:36:50,470 --> 00:36:52,100
Yes, but it's irrelevant. 是的，那不过是小菜一碟

419
00:36:52,470 --> 00:36:53,850
That's something else. 和我说的不是一回事

420
00:36:56,020 --> 00:36:57,060
Alright. 好吧

421
00:37:02,980 --> 00:37:03,940
Sorry. 不好意思

422
00:37:06,740 --> 00:37:09,030
It's intrusive. We don't know each other. 有点唐突了，我们还不算认识

423
00:37:09,150 --> 00:37:10,370
No problem. 没问题

424
00:37:11,320 --> 00:37:14,330
- My actual first name is Prairie. - Sorry? -实际上我的名字叫普莱丽 -啥？

425
00:37:14,910 --> 00:37:18,830
My parents thought it was a typically French name. 我父母觉得这是个典型的法国名字

426
00:37:18,960 --> 00:37:22,080
In fact, it sounds weird. So here I go by Diane. 实际上，它听起来怪怪的，所以我干脆叫戴安娜了

427
00:37:22,250 --> 00:37:23,340
Prairie? 普莱丽？

428
00:37:27,720 --> 00:37:28,630
Alright. 好吧

429
00:37:37,100 --> 00:37:38,520
Sorry, what did... 不好意思，那个……

430
00:37:39,810 --> 00:37:40,810
I can't... 我做不到……

431
00:37:41,650 --> 00:37:42,730
hear a thing. 我听到了什么

432
00:37:53,700 --> 00:37:56,120
<i>The military is redeploying defence forces</i> 军队正在重新部署防御部队

433
00:37:56,290 --> 00:37:59,000
<i>with the mobilisation of three infantry regiments.</i> 动员了三个步兵团

434
00:37:59,160 --> 00:38:02,210
<i>Two squadrons of fighter pilots are on constant alert.</i> 两个战斗飞行中队时刻保持预警

435
00:38:02,380 --> 00:38:06,000
<i>A nuclear ballistic missile submarine ill soon leave port.</i> 一艘核弹道导弹潜艇将很快离开港口

436
00:38:06,130 --> 00:38:09,130
<i>Its departure from Brest is imminent</i> 它即将离开布雷斯特

437
00:38:09,260 --> 00:38:11,050
<i>and its route is top secret.</i> 航线线路属于机密

438
00:38:11,220 --> 00:38:14,350
<i>Michael, can Europe assure its own defence?</i> 迈克尔，欧洲能保证自己的防御吗

439
00:38:14,510 --> 00:38:15,850
<i>That's the big question.</i> 这是个大问题

440
00:38:16,010 --> 00:38:18,640
<i>Many wonder if Finland is worth dying for.</i> 很多人想知道芬兰是否值得为之牺牲

441
00:38:18,810 --> 00:38:20,730
<i>The President has made a decision.</i> 总统已做出决定

442
00:38:20,890 --> 00:38:24,400
<i>"It is not a question of dying for Finland,</i> 这不是为芬兰牺牲的问题了

443
00:38:24,520 --> 00:38:26,650
<i>"but saving the very idea of Europe,"</i> 而是拯救欧洲的概念

444
00:38:26,820 --> 00:38:29,740
<i>he declared a few hours ago at the Brussels summit.</i> 他几个小时以前就已经在布鲁塞尔宣布了

445
00:38:47,630 --> 00:38:49,670
So that's acoustic warfare. 这就是声学战

446
00:40:38,700 --> 00:40:42,120
I'm trying to get my head around you living in there. 我想让你知道我住在那里

447
00:40:43,990 --> 00:40:46,250
Stroke of luck, meeting me. 运气好，见到我了

448
00:40:49,790 --> 00:40:52,420
Thank goodness we couldn't find your Maths book. 谢天谢地，我们找不到你的数学书。

449
00:40:54,670 --> 00:40:55,760
Hold on... 等一下

450
00:40:57,260 --> 00:40:59,640
You knew all along you didn't have it? 你本来就知道没那本书？

451
00:41:00,050 --> 00:41:01,350
You planned it. 你故意的

452
00:41:02,140 --> 00:41:03,010
What? 啥？

453
00:41:03,180 --> 00:41:04,140
No. 不是的

454
00:41:05,220 --> 00:41:06,770
It was in my database. 我数据库里有

455
00:41:09,100 --> 00:41:12,360
We never clear the database, that's the problem. 我们从不盘点数据库，这才是问题

456
00:41:17,320 --> 00:41:18,700
You don't believe me? 你不信？

457
00:41:19,990 --> 00:41:22,780
We have a procedure that deletes automatically. 我们会有一个自动删除的进程

458
00:41:24,290 --> 00:41:26,120
A procedure to delete what? 删除什么的进程？

459
00:41:26,910 --> 00:41:28,160
Books? 书吗？

460
00:41:29,750 --> 00:41:31,250
Dismantled submarines. 拆掉的潜艇

461
00:41:32,080 --> 00:41:34,630
They're deleted from the operational database. 会把它们从操作数据库中删除。

462
00:41:47,430 --> 00:41:49,520
But not from the physical archives. 但不包括物理档案

463
00:42:46,240 --> 00:42:47,870
EX-SOVIET BLOC 前苏联集团

464
00:43:31,870 --> 00:43:33,040
That's it. 就是它了

465
00:43:46,050 --> 00:43:47,260
Paired double prop. 双叶双桨

466
00:43:48,140 --> 00:43:50,560
That explains the four blades and the transient. 这就是那个时候四桨叶的解释

467
00:43:53,270 --> 00:43:54,560
<i>Timour III.</i> 帝汶III号

468
00:43:55,230 --> 00:43:56,520
The Soviet terror. 苏联的恐怖

469
00:43:59,610 --> 00:44:01,400
The hell they scrapped it. 他妈的他们把它扔掉了

470
00:44:09,490 --> 00:44:11,200
You're out of your mind. 你疯了吧

471
00:44:12,450 --> 00:44:13,330
Captain... 长官

472
00:44:14,250 --> 00:44:15,290
Look! 你看

473
00:44:16,120 --> 00:44:17,250
Your cellphone. 手机给我

474
00:44:24,050 --> 00:44:25,430
You are under arrest. 你被捕了

475
00:44:26,180 --> 00:44:27,300
Check that file. 看一下这个文件

476
00:44:28,220 --> 00:44:28,970
Captain! 长官

477
00:44:32,140 --> 00:44:34,100
The transient is not a drone. 那个时候的不是无人潜艇

478
00:44:35,100 --> 00:44:37,810
It's a Russian nuclear sub.<i> Timour III</i>. 是俄罗斯核潜艇帝汶III号

479
00:44:37,940 --> 00:44:40,110
Four blades, the same transient. 四桨叶，转瞬即逝

480
00:44:40,230 --> 00:44:42,320
Identical acoustic signatures. 一样的声音信号

481
00:44:47,110 --> 00:44:49,910
Including the asymmetry due to shaft wear. 包括轴磨损引起的不对称。

482
00:44:52,450 --> 00:44:54,540
Decommissioned years ago, in theory. 几年前就退役了，不过是在理论上

483
00:44:54,700 --> 00:44:56,710
In fact stowed away by the Russians. 实际上是俄罗斯人接手了

484
00:44:56,870 --> 00:44:59,920
Until deletion from our database by the procedure. 而程序把它从数据库删掉了

485
00:45:00,380 --> 00:45:02,040
And years later, there it is. 几年后的今天，它又出现了

486
00:45:02,500 --> 00:45:03,550
Untouched. 完好无损

487
00:45:04,000 --> 00:45:05,720
Unclassified, incognito. 无法确认，隐藏起来

488
00:45:08,010 --> 00:45:09,090
Captain! 长官

489
00:45:19,400 --> 00:45:20,360
Shit! 妈的

490
00:45:45,880 --> 00:45:47,720
Your analysis checks out. 你的分析结果出来了

491
00:45:48,670 --> 00:45:52,600
The Brits faced the same rogue situation, same transient. 英国人面临过同样被骗的情况，一样的转瞬即逝

492
00:45:52,720 --> 00:45:55,640
Cross-referencing data leads us to the <i>Timour III</i>. 交互数据将我们引向帝汶III号

493
00:45:56,390 --> 00:45:58,850
Which sheds a different light on your conduct, 也对你之前的行为做出宽恕

494
00:45:59,180 --> 00:46:01,810
even if it remains technically reprehensible. 即使实际上你该受到谴责

495
00:46:04,110 --> 00:46:06,860
After discussions with the Admiral, 经过和上将的讨论

496
00:46:08,610 --> 00:46:10,240
this goes no further. 下不为例

497
00:46:11,030 --> 00:46:12,110
This time. 不过这次

498
00:46:13,410 --> 00:46:14,830
It rankles to tell you, 我很恼火的告诉你

499
00:46:14,990 --> 00:46:17,950
but you may end up on a nuclear ballistic missile sub. 你要到弹道核潜艇上去了

500
00:46:19,040 --> 00:46:21,460
<i>Formidable</i>'s captain wants you aboard. 无畏号的舰长要你上船

501
00:46:23,380 --> 00:46:25,500
<i>Formidable</i>'s captain wants me? 无畏号舰长要我？

502
00:46:27,210 --> 00:46:28,380
I don't know him. 我不认识他

503
00:46:28,510 --> 00:46:30,220
The new one, you do. 新任舰长，你认识

504
00:46:31,130 --> 00:46:32,220
Grandchamp. 格兰夏普

505
00:46:35,180 --> 00:46:37,270
He threw a hissy fit to get you. 他吵着要你

506
00:46:41,690 --> 00:46:44,150
Don't get over-excited. There's a test first. 别兴奋过头了，你得先通过测试

507
00:46:44,730 --> 00:46:46,650
The Admiral has the last word. 上将最后说了

508
00:46:47,360 --> 00:46:49,400
Get into uniform. Training starts today. 穿上制服，今天就开始训练

509
00:46:50,530 --> 00:46:51,490
Yes, sir. 是，长官

510
00:47:18,310 --> 00:47:21,140
Russian sonar, low frequency. Type Shark. 俄罗斯声纳，低频，代码鲨鱼

511
00:47:21,270 --> 00:47:22,350
Vessel? 是船吗？

512
00:47:22,480 --> 00:47:23,810
K-138.

513
00:47:23,980 --> 00:47:25,270
New generation. 最新一代

514
00:47:27,150 --> 00:47:28,860
Plus five dolphins, two babies. 另外有五只海豚，两个孩子

515
00:47:47,170 --> 00:47:48,000
Something there. 有东西

516
00:47:50,880 --> 00:47:51,920
Submarine. 潜艇

517
00:47:53,630 --> 00:47:54,510
Nuclear propulsion. 核动力

518
00:47:54,630 --> 00:47:55,760
Attack submarine. 攻击型潜艇

519
00:47:56,930 --> 00:47:57,930
Not American. 不是美国的

520
00:47:58,640 --> 00:47:59,680
Not British. 也不是英国的

521
00:48:03,480 --> 00:48:04,810
It could be the <i>Kiev.</i> 可能是基辅级

522
00:48:06,600 --> 00:48:08,980
No, there's an egg-whisk tone. 不对，有打蛋器的声音

523
00:48:16,360 --> 00:48:18,450
Nuclear ballistic missile submarine. 核弹道潜艇

524
00:48:18,620 --> 00:48:19,780
SSBN.

525
00:48:21,080 --> 00:48:22,160
Before going stealth. 还没开始秘密行动

526
00:48:22,290 --> 00:48:25,540
If it had gone stealth, you wouldn't hear it, Socks. 如果它开始行动了，你是听不到的，小鬼

527
00:48:25,670 --> 00:48:28,000
Even the machine wouldn't detect it. 甚至连仪器都探测不到

528
00:48:28,790 --> 00:48:29,670
Anyway... 这么说吧

529
00:48:30,170 --> 00:48:31,380
FYI, it's... 如果确认的话，他是……

530
00:48:31,550 --> 00:48:32,550
<i>Formidable.</i> 无畏号

531
00:48:33,260 --> 00:48:34,380
Really? 确定吗？

532
00:48:35,050 --> 00:48:36,300
Not <i>Invincible</i>? 不是无敌号吗？

533
00:48:37,260 --> 00:48:39,390
They're identical, constructed together. 他们是同型号的，一起建造的

534
00:48:39,550 --> 00:48:42,640
Check spectral analysis. <i>Formidable</i> first. 比对频谱的话，优先判断是无畏号

535
00:48:43,060 --> 00:48:44,770
Then the other. 那么其他的呢？

536
00:48:47,600 --> 00:48:49,230
You see any difference? 你发现了什么不同？

537
00:49:32,190 --> 00:49:35,530
Was <i>Formidable</i>'s turbine remachined due to damage? 无畏号的涡轮是不是损坏了重新加工过？

538
00:49:42,200 --> 00:49:43,490
The dream team. 梦之队

539
00:49:43,620 --> 00:49:45,040
- Ok, Socks? - D'Orsi. -好了吗？小鬼？ -多西

540
00:49:45,450 --> 00:49:46,950
Sorry, admiral, didn't see you. 对不起，上将，没看到你在

541
00:49:48,000 --> 00:49:48,750
Well... 好吧……

542
00:49:50,330 --> 00:49:52,840
Chanteraide, confirmed. Boarding tomorrow, 4 am. 尚特莱，确认，明早四点登艇

543
00:49:53,380 --> 00:49:54,340
Well played, son. 干得漂亮，孩子

544
00:49:56,340 --> 00:49:58,550
- You did your medical? - All good. -你体检过了吗？ -没问题

545
00:49:58,720 --> 00:50:00,390
Not on antidepressants? 没吃什么抗抑郁药吗？

546
00:50:01,220 --> 00:50:02,930
Shows up in your urine. 有尿检呢

547
00:50:03,100 --> 00:50:04,390
The SSBN 弹道导弹核潜艇

548
00:50:04,510 --> 00:50:05,930
isn't the Love Boat. 不是有爱的潜艇

549
00:50:06,850 --> 00:50:11,020
The mission is, ready to fire in under an hour on presidential orders. 其任务就是等待总统的指令，随时准备开火

550
00:50:12,520 --> 00:50:14,940
You're the country's life insurance. 你们是国家的安全保障

551
00:50:16,820 --> 00:50:17,900
Copy that. 明白

552
00:50:18,280 --> 00:50:21,160
3,000 years of civilisation did not bring peace. 3000年的文明没有带来和平

553
00:50:21,780 --> 00:50:23,030
Only deterrence... 只有威慑……

554
00:50:23,370 --> 00:50:25,490
Effective deterrence depends on 有效的威慑取决于

555
00:50:26,330 --> 00:50:27,660
sailors keeping quiet. 水手们保持安静

556
00:50:28,500 --> 00:50:30,790
"Diwel didrouz maro pa denn." 迪威尔·迪德罗兹·马罗·帕丹。

557
00:50:32,120 --> 00:50:33,130
What's that? 啥意思

558
00:50:33,250 --> 00:50:34,630
The SSBN motto. SSBN的座右铭

559
00:50:35,130 --> 00:50:36,170
Your new home. 你的新去处会告诉你

560
00:50:37,550 --> 00:50:40,220
"Invisible and silent, I bring death." 隐形消声，我是死神

561
00:50:42,470 --> 00:50:43,720
Good luck, son. 祝你好运，小鬼

562
00:50:45,350 --> 00:50:46,640
Keep on the PIM. 保持联络

563
00:51:56,750 --> 00:51:57,750
Captain. 长官

564
00:51:58,090 --> 00:51:59,340
<i>Titan</i>, red company. 泰坦号，红队

565
00:51:59,750 --> 00:52:00,840
Attention! 注意

566
00:52:02,090 --> 00:52:03,220
Eyes front. 向前看

567
00:52:06,220 --> 00:52:09,010
Company mustered and correct. At your command, sir. 所有成员到齐，等待命令，长官

568
00:52:10,600 --> 00:52:11,810
Welcome aboard. 欢迎上船

569
00:52:42,380 --> 00:52:44,510
<i>Formidable</i> blue company, attention! 无畏号，蓝队，注意

570
00:52:53,430 --> 00:52:54,310
XO, 传令官

571
00:52:54,980 --> 00:52:56,140
take over. 接管

572
00:53:36,390 --> 00:53:37,640
XO, take over. 传令官，接管

573
00:53:38,890 --> 00:53:39,900
At ease. 稍息

574
00:53:40,730 --> 00:53:41,900
Attention! 注意

575
00:53:42,060 --> 00:53:44,860
Roll call. Respond present and board. 点名，报到后上船

576
00:53:45,030 --> 00:53:46,190
- Abbad! - Present. -阿巴德 -到

577
00:53:46,360 --> 00:53:47,490
- Aboulker! - Present. -阿博尔科 -到

578
00:54:02,540 --> 00:54:05,380
The doc found cannabis in your urine sample. 医生在你的尿样中发现大麻

579
00:54:11,220 --> 00:54:13,050
He declared you unfit to serve. 他觉得你不适合随舰

580
00:54:19,140 --> 00:54:20,850
I will not challenge it. 我不打算反驳

581
00:54:22,900 --> 00:54:26,530
I must be able to rely on each man operating at 100%. 我必须100%信赖每个人

582
00:54:44,380 --> 00:54:46,630
Captain Grandchamp aboard! 格兰夏普船长登艇

583
00:57:02,310 --> 00:57:03,470
Stop! Gates closing. 停下，关门了

584
00:57:03,600 --> 00:57:04,980
Fortress procedure! 进入要塞

585
00:57:08,980 --> 00:57:10,480
Loc, give me a hand! 洛克，帮我一把

586
00:57:25,000 --> 00:57:26,210
Move! 行动

587
00:57:27,160 --> 00:57:28,370
Coming through. 快来

588
00:57:28,540 --> 00:57:31,170
- What's going on? - Nuke R-30. Fired from Bering Sea. -怎么回事？ -核弹R-30，从白令海发射了

589
00:57:55,110 --> 00:57:56,740
The Russians are moving! 俄国人行动了

590
00:57:57,190 --> 00:57:58,570
Keep the info coming. 保持信息跟进

591
00:57:59,110 --> 00:58:00,160
Faster! 快！

592
00:58:01,570 --> 00:58:02,740
President's office. 总统办公室

593
00:58:06,040 --> 00:58:08,790
The President is at Jupiter Command. 总统在木星指挥部

594
00:58:08,910 --> 00:58:10,790
Upgrade to alert level 10. 警报提升至10级

595
00:58:11,460 --> 00:58:14,130
Tell Grandchamp to go stealth immediately. 让格兰夏普立刻开始潜航

596
00:58:16,760 --> 00:58:18,220
Keep the info coming! 继续跟进信息

597
00:58:19,170 --> 00:58:20,550
25 minutes left. 只有25分钟了

598
00:58:27,810 --> 00:58:29,060
FORTRESS PROCEDURE ACTIVATED 要塞程序启动

599
00:58:35,610 --> 00:58:37,610
<i>Formidable</i> at 6,000 m, opening. 无畏号，距离6000米，打开。

600
00:58:37,780 --> 00:58:38,820
Copy. 收到

601
00:58:39,360 --> 00:58:40,280
Very good. 很好

602
00:58:40,450 --> 00:58:42,070
What's that trace, north? 那是什么痕迹，北面？

603
00:58:43,530 --> 00:58:44,700
Nothing. The 15. 没什么，15号

604
00:58:45,200 --> 00:58:46,450
Identify contact 11. 确认连接11号

605
00:58:46,620 --> 00:58:48,250
We have 11, bearing 2-3-9. 11号在线，位置2-3-9

606
00:58:49,200 --> 00:58:50,460
Echo, Foxtrot. E，F

607
00:58:52,290 --> 00:58:54,080
Echo, X-ray. E，X

608
00:58:55,460 --> 00:58:57,300
<i>Formidable</i> assuming stealth mode, 无畏号进入潜航模式了

609
00:58:57,460 --> 00:59:00,050
thanks us for our company and wishes us the best. 感谢我们的陪伴，并祝我们一切顺利

610
00:59:00,220 --> 00:59:03,180
Salute<i> Formidable</i>'s formidability and wish her well. 敬礼，也祝无畏号一切顺利

611
00:59:03,300 --> 00:59:04,300
Copy, captain. 收到，长官

612
00:59:04,470 --> 00:59:05,890
Plotting priority on 12. 优先标绘12号

613
00:59:06,010 --> 00:59:08,470
Mission accomplished.No further instructions. 任务完成，没有进一步指示

614
00:59:08,850 --> 00:59:10,850
If not on watch, stand down. 如果不在值班的，就下来吧

615
00:59:11,980 --> 00:59:13,190
Guys... 伙计们……

616
00:59:13,850 --> 00:59:16,150
Now or never for a workout or shower. 做做锻炼或者洗个澡

617
00:59:16,320 --> 00:59:17,400
Or even both. 也可以两样一起

618
00:59:17,900 --> 00:59:19,030
In the right order. 不过别弄错顺序

619
00:59:22,990 --> 00:59:25,200
<i>Formidable</i>, bearing 0-2-3. Losing her. 无畏号，位置0-2-3，消失了

620
01:00:01,360 --> 01:00:04,070
