- Don't crack! - Cut it out! -别开玩笑！ -别说了！

808
01:12:24,520 --> 01:12:26,020
You think I don't know? 你以为我不知道？

809
01:12:26,150 --> 01:12:28,690
<i>Formidable</i>'s gone stealth. We've no idea where. 无畏号在潜航，而我们束手无策

810
01:12:28,860 --> 01:12:32,150
It just went stealth. It can't be far from <i>Titan</i>. 它刚开始潜航，距离泰号坦应该不远

811
01:12:32,280 --> 01:12:34,320
No sonar can detect it. 声纳探测不到它

812
01:12:34,490 --> 01:12:35,780
What do you suggest? 你有什么建议

813
01:12:44,830 --> 01:12:45,790
It's now, admiral. 上将，就是现在了

814
01:12:45,960 --> 01:12:47,080
No, admiral. 不，上将

815
01:13:23,120 --> 01:13:26,080
Couldn't you wear normal shoes on a day like this? 像今天这样的日子你就不能穿一双普通的鞋？

816
01:13:30,040 --> 01:13:31,300
Base was out of them? 哪怕是基地在外面？

817
01:13:34,420 --> 01:13:35,760
Going to the dogs. 还真是形影不离

818
01:13:37,300 --> 01:13:39,430
Not surprising coming from you. 你一点也不惊讶

819
01:13:40,260 --> 01:13:43,140
Didn't you spend three months in a sub in your socks? 你在那艘潜艇里当了三个月的小鬼？

820
01:13:46,690 --> 01:13:48,810
You certainly earned your nickname. 看来你的绰号改不了了

821
01:13:49,980 --> 01:13:52,150
Nice. What goes around comes around. 很好，什么事都会发生

822
01:13:54,440 --> 01:13:56,070
<i>Admiral, this is CIRA.</i> 上将，这里是CIRA

823
01:13:56,530 --> 01:13:58,570
<i>R-30 impact in the Compigne forest.</i> R-30落在了森林里

824
01:13:59,070 --> 01:14:00,490
<i>No damage reported.</i> 没有造成打击损失

825
01:14:00,660 --> 01:14:02,160
<i>No nuclear warhead.</i> 也没有核弹头

826
01:15:06,850 --> 01:15:09,520
Admiral, to what do I owe the honour? 上将，什么风把你吹来了

827
01:15:10,060 --> 01:15:12,480
To all hands, this is Alfost! 所有人注意，我是阿尔弗斯特

828
01:15:13,020 --> 01:15:14,610
We fell into a trap. 我们中了圈套

829
01:15:14,980 --> 01:15:18,240
<i>Formidable</i> was ordered to fire a nuclear missile at Russia. 无畏号被派往俄罗斯发射核弹

830
01:15:18,740 --> 01:15:21,360
If the missile is launched, the Russians counter. 如果导弹发射，俄国人还击

831
01:15:21,530 --> 01:15:23,030
I'll let you join the dots. 那么一切都晚了

832
01:15:24,330 --> 01:15:28,040
What I'm about to say is hard to take in, and harder to say. 我要说的难以做到，更难以置信

833
01:15:28,830 --> 01:15:31,580
Our priority is to stop Grandchamp launching. 我们的首要任务是阻止格兰夏普的发射

834
01:15:32,500 --> 01:15:34,040
By all means necessary. 以所有的可能

835
01:15:35,340 --> 01:15:37,460
This defies procedure, why trust you? 这不符合程序，为什么相信你

836
01:15:55,520 --> 01:15:57,020
Your Captain speaking. 我是船长

837
01:15:58,980 --> 01:16:00,400
Action stations! 开始行动

838
01:16:01,200 --> 01:16:02,490
In position. 各就各位

839
01:16:04,620 --> 01:16:06,780
<i>Formidable</i>'s last known position? 无畏号最后已知的位置在哪？

840
01:16:07,330 --> 01:16:09,040
They went stealth in sector 7. 他们在7区开始潜航了

841
01:16:09,200 --> 01:16:10,200
Sector 7? 7区？

842
01:16:13,210 --> 01:16:14,960
In his shoes, where'd you go? 他走了，你们准备去哪？

843
01:16:15,130 --> 01:16:16,670
Grandchamp is pure reason. 格兰夏普的理由很简单

844
01:16:16,790 --> 01:16:18,590
He calculates for optimal outcomes. 他计算出最佳结果

845
01:16:18,750 --> 01:16:20,260
Optimal in this case? 当前情况下最佳的？

846
01:16:20,420 --> 01:16:22,970
First up, whatever saves lives. 无论如何，救人第一

847
01:16:23,130 --> 01:16:25,010
Saves lives? Meaning? 救人？什么意思？

848
01:16:28,810 --> 01:16:30,390
With nuclear missiles, 用核弹头

849
01:16:30,680 --> 01:16:34,140
to avoid collateral damage you reset position at launch? 为了避免附带的损害，你在发射时重置了位置？

850
01:16:35,310 --> 01:16:37,060
It's not protocol but... 这个没有规定，不过……

851
01:16:38,520 --> 01:16:42,240
To keep the hit clean, it's best to fix position before launch. 为了保持命中率，最好在发射前确定位置

852
01:16:43,150 --> 01:16:44,070
He'll do that. 他会这么做的

853
01:16:44,200 --> 01:16:45,240
For sure. 可以肯定

854
01:16:46,910 --> 01:16:48,490
But he can't surface. 但是他不能浮出水面

855
01:16:50,500 --> 01:16:51,950
He needs a magic point. 他需要一个悬浮点

856
01:16:52,120 --> 01:16:53,910
Bring up nearby magic points. 最近的悬浮点在哪？

857
01:16:54,080 --> 01:16:56,790
- Magic points? - True, we don't have them. -悬浮点？ -实际上，这条船上没有相关资料

858
01:16:57,130 --> 01:16:58,170
Only SSNBs do. 只有弹道核潜艇上才能找到

859
01:16:59,500 --> 01:17:01,590
I commanded an SSNB. I need to remember. 我指挥过核潜艇，我得回忆一下

860
01:17:01,760 --> 01:17:02,840
Sector 7. 7区

861
01:17:03,010 --> 01:17:04,760
Sector 8, two of them. 8区，有两个

862
01:17:04,930 --> 01:17:06,050
Mapped peaks. 绘制峰值

863
01:17:06,180 --> 01:17:08,100
Calypso here and Circe here. 卡莉普索在这里，瑟曦在这里

864
01:17:08,220 --> 01:17:09,390
ETA? 预计到达时间？

865
01:17:10,930 --> 01:17:12,680
Calypso, for him, ten minutes. 卡莉普索，对他来说，需要十分钟

866
01:17:13,850 --> 01:17:14,980
For us, 13. 而我们需要13分钟

867
01:17:15,140 --> 01:17:16,980
- Too late. - Circe... -太晚了 -瑟曦……

868
01:17:17,900 --> 01:17:19,730
We arrive pretty much simultaneously. 我们几乎同时到达

869
01:17:19,900 --> 01:17:21,530
We need him to go for Circe. 我们得让他们去瑟曦

870
01:17:21,980 --> 01:17:23,240
Circe. 瑟曦

871
01:17:25,530 --> 01:17:27,280
- Chops... - Admiral? -通讯员 -在，上将

872
01:17:28,120 --> 01:17:30,950
Transmit to base to send two aircraft over Calypso. 联系基地派两架飞机去卡莉普索

873
01:17:31,120 --> 01:17:34,330
They cover the sea with sonobuoys and crank it up. 让他们用声纳覆盖海面，调高音量

874
01:17:34,460 --> 01:17:36,290
See if the octopuses like AC/DC. 看看章鱼是不是像AC/DC

875
01:17:36,420 --> 01:17:37,330
Yes, sir. 是，长官

876
01:17:37,630 --> 01:17:40,000
Transmitting code 5, confirmed Alfost. 联络代码5，确认阿尔弗斯特

877
01:17:45,170 --> 01:17:47,050
Grandchamp winds up in a moshpit 格兰夏普进了一个舞池

878
01:17:47,800 --> 01:17:49,850
and has to swing over to Circe. 就不得不往瑟曦去

879
01:17:50,890 --> 01:17:52,640
XO, take us to Circe. 传令官，去瑟曦

880
01:17:52,810 --> 01:17:53,850
Romeo. 罗密欧

881
01:17:54,140 --> 01:17:55,560
Plotter, bearing to Circe? 绘图员，给我瑟曦的位置

882
01:17:57,100 --> 01:17:57,980
Alpha.

883
01:17:58,100 --> 01:17:59,440
2-3-2.

884
01:18:02,190 --> 01:18:04,610
CALYPSO MAGIC POINT 47N 8W 卡莉普索悬浮点 47N 8W

885
01:18:23,550 --> 01:18:24,380
Analysis? 分析结果如何？

886
01:18:24,550 --> 01:18:26,470
Sonobuoys. Type Dicasse. 声纳浮标，迪卡西型的

887
01:18:26,630 --> 01:18:27,840
Lots of them. 有很多

888
01:18:28,010 --> 01:18:30,180
Dicasse, that's our Navy. What the hell! 迪卡西，是我们的海军，搞什么？

889
01:18:30,720 --> 01:18:32,100
It's weird. 真奇怪？

890
01:18:32,260 --> 01:18:33,930
It's gotta be Alfost. 可能是阿尔弗斯特

891
01:18:34,520 --> 01:18:35,730
Captain? 舰长？

892
01:18:37,310 --> 01:18:39,440
Distance from Magic Point 2? 距离2号悬浮点多远？

893
01:18:39,560 --> 01:18:41,310
Circe, 6,000 m at 2-8-4. 瑟曦，6000米，方位2-8-4

894
01:18:42,230 --> 01:18:43,940
Captain takes the boat. 现在船长接管

895
01:18:44,070 --> 01:18:46,070
Set course 2-8-4. Ahead 5. 坐标2-8-4，前进5

896
01:18:46,490 --> 01:18:49,150
Captain, someone's messing with us. 船长，有人在和我们捣乱

897
01:18:49,280 --> 01:18:52,490
Maybe we should fire with less precision. Time's short. 也许我们应该降低射击精度，时间不多了

898
01:18:53,410 --> 01:18:55,290
No, we continue the sequence. 不，我们按程序来

899
01:19:00,540 --> 01:19:02,670
- I'll be in position. - Very good. -那我待命 -很好

900
01:19:08,920 --> 01:19:11,300
<i>Missile room. Running checks.</i> 导弹舱，发射检查

901
01:19:29,740 --> 01:19:31,410
Magic point 2,500 m. 悬浮点2500米

902
01:19:35,870 --> 01:19:37,580
Why no insignia? 为什么不戴上徽章？

903
01:19:39,200 --> 01:19:41,420
Don't you want to die looking good? 你们不想死得漂亮点？

904
01:19:44,420 --> 01:19:47,260
What's this eyesore? You need comfort? 在这碍什么眼，你想要多舒服？

905
01:19:47,420 --> 01:19:48,920
You're ballet dancers? 你是跳芭蕾的吗？

906
01:19:53,590 --> 01:19:56,180
If the computer's bust, why isn't it replaced? 如果电脑不好使，干嘛不换一台？

907
01:19:56,350 --> 01:19:57,930
Because this is France. 法国国情

908
01:20:00,640 --> 01:20:02,100
Only one works. 就一个人干活

909
01:20:02,230 --> 01:20:04,440
Arriving at Circe. Let's reset now. 到达瑟曦，现在复位

910
01:20:04,560 --> 01:20:07,020
- Chops, take over. - Yes, sir. -通讯员，你接管。 -遵命

911
01:20:09,860 --> 01:20:11,360
Stand by to reset. 准备复位

912
01:20:11,900 --> 01:20:13,160
Ready. 就绪

913
01:20:14,110 --> 01:20:15,450
Reset. 复位

914
01:20:26,460 --> 01:20:27,590
Reset complete. 重置完成

915
01:20:27,750 --> 01:20:29,630
Position margin of error, 100 m. 位置误差范围，100米

916
01:20:29,800 --> 01:20:31,340
Optimal margin reached. 已到达最佳发射位置

917
01:20:31,470 --> 01:20:34,970
Attain launch depth. When we're there, we fire the missile. 调整发射深度，到位后发射导弹

918
01:20:38,890 --> 01:20:40,480
Waking missile. 导弹启动

919
01:20:42,810 --> 01:20:45,810
Magic point 1,000 m. Entering reset zone. 悬浮点1000米，正在通过复位区域

920
01:20:45,940 --> 01:20:47,980
At this distance, try the underwater phone. 保持这个距离，试试用水下电话

921
01:20:48,110 --> 01:20:49,320
Wait! 等一下

922
01:20:50,360 --> 01:20:54,030
Do that and it's simple. They'll hear and locate us. 那样做很简单，他们会听到并找到我们

923
01:20:54,150 --> 01:20:56,910
Either they answer or they apply protocol 然后要么回答，要么按照规定程序

924
01:20:57,030 --> 01:20:58,660
and torpedo us. 向我们发射鱼雷

925
01:20:58,780 --> 01:21:00,330
Stand by to engage. 准备接触

926
01:21:01,620 --> 01:21:03,250
Heuristic, as methods go. 没有别的办法了？

927
01:21:03,960 --> 01:21:05,080
Quit the philosophy. 要么别干了

928
01:21:06,130 --> 01:21:07,500
Yes, sir. 遵命，长官

929
01:21:08,710 --> 01:21:10,050
But it's Grandchamp. 可那是格兰夏普

930
01:21:11,840 --> 01:21:14,380
- Torpedo, prepare to fire. - Copy. -鱼雷准备发射 -收到

931
01:21:16,800 --> 01:21:18,720
Tubes one to four ready. 1-4号鱼雷准备就绪

932
01:21:19,640 --> 01:21:21,140
Transmitting by TUUM. 通过TUUM频段传输

933
01:21:21,310 --> 01:21:22,310
Copy that. TUUM. 收到，TUUM

934
01:21:22,480 --> 01:21:25,020
As soon as you hear a sound, give the alert. 一听到声音，就给出警告

935
01:21:25,140 --> 01:21:26,100
Copy. 收到

936
01:21:41,870 --> 01:21:44,200
I have three frequencies, no bearing. 我有三个频率，没有方位

937
01:21:44,370 --> 01:21:46,210
- Check the lawn. - Marked frequencies? -检查一下海底 -标记频率

938
01:21:46,330 --> 01:21:48,540
Yes. Possible submarine. 是，可能是潜艇

939
01:21:48,710 --> 01:21:49,960
Watch out, poss-sub! 注意，疑似潜艇

940
01:21:53,670 --> 01:21:55,550
Control, get me the XO. 给我接传令官

941
01:21:56,430 --> 01:21:59,470
XO, get back here to Control. Poss-sub contact. 传令官，回控制室来，发现疑似潜艇

942
01:21:59,760 --> 01:22:01,100
<i>Copy that.</i> 收到

943
01:22:02,010 --> 01:22:03,390
Examine each trace. 诊断所有频段

944
01:22:11,940 --> 01:22:12,940
TUUM!

945
01:22:17,200 --> 01:22:18,910
The poss-sub. Plot it. 疑似潜艇，标记它

946
01:22:19,070 --> 01:22:20,990
Bearing on TUUM? Cross-check. 确定TUUM位置，用交叉法核查

947
01:22:21,160 --> 01:22:22,910
- 0-2-8. - Bearing 0-2-8! -0-2-8 -方位0-2-8

948
01:22:23,080 --> 01:22:25,040
- 1,000 m. - Torpedo standing by. -1000米 -鱼雷准备

949
01:22:25,160 --> 01:22:27,290
Bravo Charlie 3. 布拉沃查理3

950
01:22:27,710 --> 01:22:29,630
<i>This is Zulu Delta 4.</i> 我是祖鲁德塔4

951
01:22:29,750 --> 01:22:31,210
<i>Do you copy?</i> 听到吗？

952
01:22:31,380 --> 01:22:33,880
Zulu Delta 4, that's <i>Titan</i>. We take it. 祖鲁德塔4，是泰坦号，接进来

953
01:22:34,050 --> 01:22:36,970
Captain, we have orders to launch. There are rules. 船长，我们接到了发射的命令，有规定的。

954
01:22:37,090 --> 01:22:39,680
- No TUUM. - It's D'Orsi. My men! -不，TUUM -是多西，我的人

955
01:22:41,720 --> 01:22:43,720
Why's he want us to transmit? 他为什么要现在联络？

956
01:22:45,180 --> 01:22:47,480
- To detect us. - D'Orsi wouldn't do that. -来探测我们 -多西不会这么做

957
01:22:47,640 --> 01:22:49,730
Why did they surface earlier? 他们为什么这么早暴露？

958
01:22:50,190 --> 01:22:51,690
Someone boarded. Who? 有人上船了，谁？

959
01:22:51,810 --> 01:22:53,480
This is Zulu Delta 4. 我是祖鲁德塔4

960
01:22:54,280 --> 01:22:55,070
Do you copy? 听到吗？

961
01:23:00,780 --> 01:23:02,030
<i>Do you copy?</i> 听到吗？

962
01:23:04,410 --> 01:23:06,830
The President's order is irrevocable. 总统的命令是不可撤销的。

963
01:23:08,210 --> 01:23:09,790
<i>This is Zulu Delta 4.</i> 我是祖鲁德塔4

964
01:23:37,280 --> 01:23:38,570
Deactivate TUUM. 停用TUUM

965
01:23:44,530 --> 01:23:46,160
Captain to crew! 船长现在命令

966
01:23:46,700 --> 01:23:48,450
We continue launch procedure. 我们继续发射

967
01:23:51,620 --> 01:23:53,420
200 m from launch depth. 距离发射深度200米

968
01:24:04,760 --> 01:24:06,760
In any case, it's impossible. 无论如何，这不可能

969
01:24:08,970 --> 01:24:11,140
<i>Formidable</i>, stealth, Grandchamp. 无畏号，潜航，格兰夏普

970
01:24:12,940 --> 01:24:14,190
Three lemons. 三个柠檬

971
01:24:29,040 --> 01:24:31,330
Slightly stronger background noise. 略强的背景噪音

972
01:24:32,460 --> 01:24:34,210
No engine information. 没有引擎的声音

973
01:24:35,380 --> 01:24:37,300
No information is information. 没有声音就意味着……

974
01:25:22,420 --> 01:25:23,470
It's him. 是他了

975
01:25:25,430 --> 01:25:26,680
Bearing 2-3-9. 方位2-3-9

976
01:25:28,800 --> 01:25:31,680
- <i>Formidable</i> at 2-3-9. - Maximum distance 1,200 m. -无畏号方位2-3-9 -最大距离1200米

977
01:25:31,850 --> 01:25:34,520
At that distance, he heard our call. 这个距离上，他听到我们的呼叫了

978
01:25:35,190 --> 01:25:36,310
He's ready to launch. 他在准备发射

979
01:25:37,230 --> 01:25:40,150
We have no choice but to engage first. 看来没选择了，只能先发制人了

980
01:25:42,900 --> 01:25:44,110
Hold on, I... 等一下，我……

981
01:25:45,410 --> 01:25:46,450
I've lost him. 声音消失了

982
01:25:46,610 --> 01:25:47,570
Shit! 妈的

983
01:25:55,920 --> 01:25:57,330
Find him, Chanteraide. 找到它，尚特莱

984
01:25:57,710 --> 01:25:59,590
Time's burning up. Let's go! 火烧眉毛了，快啊

985
01:26:02,340 --> 01:26:03,670
Come on, Chanteraide. 来吧，尚特莱

986
01:26:04,130 --> 01:26:06,050
Death's only beauty is victory. 唯一死的漂亮的方法就是胜利

987
01:26:06,260 --> 01:26:07,640
We must engage. 我们必须先发制人

988
01:26:08,640 --> 01:26:10,050
We must engage! 我们必须先发制人

989
01:26:11,220 --> 01:26:12,560
I'm trying. 我在努力

990
01:26:14,850 --> 01:26:16,100
We must engage. 我们必须先发制人

991
01:26:18,310 --> 01:26:19,730
I can't do it. 我做不到

992
01:26:20,860 --> 01:26:22,280
Son, come back here. 孩子，回来

993
01:26:23,730 --> 01:26:25,820
Get the other AWA. Stay focused. 另找个监听的，集中注意力

994
01:26:25,990 --> 01:26:27,610
- They're our brothers. - No! -他们是我们自己人 -不！

995
01:26:27,740 --> 01:26:29,740
They're sailors with orders to launch. 他们是接到了发射指令的水手

996
01:26:29,910 --> 01:26:32,790
Come on, we have them. They're right there. 来吧，我们找到他们了，就在那里

997
01:26:35,290 --> 01:26:36,330
Come on. 来啊

998
01:26:39,960 --> 01:26:41,130
Control, 控制室

999
01:26:41,250 --> 01:26:43,630
prep torpedo tube for underwater vehicle. 为水下航行器准备鱼雷管

1000
01:26:44,130 --> 01:26:46,380
- What for? - To talk to Grandchamp. -干啥？ -去和格兰夏普谈谈

1001
01:26:46,920 --> 01:26:49,180
You knock in Morse, he lets you in? 你敲个莫尔斯码他就会让你进去？

1002
01:26:49,300 --> 01:26:51,180
Your options, besides firing? 你有别的选择吗？除了开火

1003
01:26:51,350 --> 01:26:52,850
The pressure's too extreme. 压力太大了

1004
01:26:53,010 --> 01:26:55,060
<i>Titan</i> submariners love pressure. 泰坦号的船员就喜欢压力

1005
01:26:55,220 --> 01:26:56,930
Bullshit! This is real life! 扯淡，现实一点

1006
01:26:57,100 --> 01:26:59,270
With that logic in Syria, we'd be dead. 都那么想的话，我们在叙利亚就已经死了

1007
01:27:00,100 --> 01:27:01,520
I know what I'm doing. 我知道我在干嘛

1008
01:27:03,230 --> 01:27:04,900
Take care of <i>Titan</i>. 照看好泰坦号

1009
01:27:05,490 --> 01:27:06,990
They're my children, too. 他们也是我的孩子

1010
01:27:14,740 --> 01:27:15,870
D'Orsi. 多西

1011
01:27:18,580 --> 01:27:19,710
Good luck. 祝你好运

1012
01:27:26,920 --> 01:27:27,840
Track him. 跟着他

1013
01:27:28,010 --> 01:27:29,340
Stay focused. Come on! 给我全神贯注

1014
01:27:31,340 --> 01:27:34,970
Delta section, prep vehicle. No questions asked. 三角区，准备潜水器，别多问

1015
01:28:37,450 --> 01:28:38,410
Last chance. 最后的机会

1016
01:29:08,730 --> 01:29:11,320
Very strange noise, bearing 0-1-5. 很奇怪的噪音，方位0-1-5

1017
01:29:11,490 --> 01:29:13,320
Like a propeller with flippers. 像一个带鳍的螺旋桨

1018
01:29:16,450 --> 01:29:17,700
A combat swimmer. 战斗蛙人

1019
01:29:18,030 --> 01:29:21,450
Clearly, <i>Titan </i>is hostile and its manoeuvres are offensive. 很明朗了，泰坦号是敌人，它采取的是攻击行动

1020
01:29:21,580 --> 01:29:22,870
We must engage. 我们得还击

1021
01:29:24,620 --> 01:29:25,630
Captain? 船长？

1022
01:29:36,430 --> 01:29:37,510
Torpedoes ready. 鱼雷准备

1023
01:29:38,600 --> 01:29:40,600
Standing by to engage, captain. 准备开火，船长

1024
01:29:44,180 --> 01:29:45,230
Engage <i>Titan</i>! 向泰坦号发射

1025
01:30:33,320 --> 01:30:34,610
Fire! 着火了

1026
01:30:34,900 --> 01:30:36,110
Delta section! 三角区

1027
01:30:37,450 --> 01:30:39,490
Fire in Delta section! 三角区着火了

1028
01:30:41,200 --> 01:30:42,910
Masks on! 戴面具

1029
01:31:05,850 --> 01:31:07,850
Admiral, hull's intact. 上将，船体没受损

1030
01:31:08,310 --> 01:31:10,810
We're watertight but fire in Delta section. 水密没问题，不过三角区着火了

1031
01:31:10,980 --> 01:31:12,730
Send more men to Delta. 多派些人去三角区

1032
01:31:13,070 --> 01:31:15,400
- We've lost <i>Formidable</i>. - White noise. -无畏号跟丢了 -白噪音

1033
01:31:15,570 --> 01:31:16,900
Need a fixed position! 需要修正位置

1034
01:31:19,240 --> 01:31:20,280
Where's D'Orsi? 多西哪儿去了？

1035
01:32:03,530 --> 01:32:05,700
<i>Only your ears can save us.</i> 只有你的耳朵能救我们了

1036
01:32:25,760 --> 01:32:27,100
<i>I trust you.</i> 我相信你

1037
01:32:33,440 --> 01:32:35,650
Chanteraide! Breathe! 尚特莱，深呼吸

1038
01:32:58,050 --> 01:32:59,210
Inserting splice. 插入接头

1039
01:32:59,380 --> 01:33:00,340
All clear? 都准备好了？

1040
01:33:00,510 --> 01:33:01,510
Standing by. 待命

1041
01:33:01,920 --> 01:33:03,050
Very good. 很好

1042
01:33:14,810 --> 01:33:15,810
Weapons officer? 武器员？

1043
01:33:15,980 --> 01:33:17,440
When you're ready, sir. 就等你了，长官

1044
01:33:19,230 --> 01:33:20,860
Control, this is XO. 控制室，我是传令官

1045
01:33:21,030 --> 01:33:22,990
Ready to enter President's code. 准备输入总统代码

1046
01:33:23,150 --> 01:33:24,030
Copy that. 收到

1047
01:33:24,740 --> 01:33:25,660
Captain, 船长

1048
01:33:25,780 --> 01:33:27,030
when you're ready. 等你下令

1049
01:33:58,440 --> 01:34:00,730
<i>Countdown to enter President's code.</i> 输入总统代码倒计时

1050
01:34:08,280 --> 01:34:09,990
Ten... Nine... 10……9……

1051
01:34:18,500 --> 01:34:20,210
Enter President's code. 输入总统代码

1052
01:34:24,760 --> 01:34:25,930
Code confirmed. 代码确认

1053
01:34:27,590 --> 01:34:28,970
Code confirmed. 代码确认

1054
01:35:08,680 --> 01:35:09,510
Three minutes! 三分钟

1055
01:35:09,680 --> 01:35:10,550
Let's go. 来吧

1056
01:35:16,100 --> 01:35:17,060
Silence! 安静

1057
01:35:24,730 --> 01:35:27,070
Missile alignment underway. Maintain course. 导弹对准进行中，保持航向。

1058
01:35:27,570 --> 01:35:30,030
- I repeat, maintain course. - Copy. -重复，保持航向 -收到

1059
01:35:30,160 --> 01:35:31,410
Helm is at 2-7-0. 航向保持2-7-0

1060
01:35:31,570 --> 01:35:32,780
Open missile door! 打开导弹舱

1061
01:35:33,120 --> 01:35:34,080
Copy. 收到

1062
01:35:58,140 --> 01:35:59,390
Torpedo. 鱼雷

1063
01:36:02,810 --> 01:36:03,730
Torpedo alert! 鱼雷警报

1064
01:36:06,650 --> 01:36:08,900
Fired by <i>Titan</i>. Captain, break away. 是泰坦号发射的，船长，得撤了

1065
01:36:09,570 --> 01:36:11,660
Negative. Alignment underway. 不行，正在进行校准

1066
01:36:12,740 --> 01:36:14,580
- How long to launch? - 160 secs! -还有多久发射 -160 秒

1067
01:36:15,240 --> 01:36:17,660
- How long to torpedo impact? - 120 secs. -鱼雷要多久 -120秒

1068
01:36:17,830 --> 01:36:20,330
- Torpedo is wire-guided. - We must break away. -鱼雷有引导线 -我们必须得撤了

1069
01:36:22,670 --> 01:36:24,590
Let's make that wire snap. Torpedo! 把线打断，发射鱼雷

1070
01:36:25,000 --> 01:36:26,420
Engage<i> Titan</i>! 射击，泰坦

1071
01:36:26,840 --> 01:36:28,670
Urgent launch, tube 2! 紧急启动，2号鱼雷管

1072
01:36:28,800 --> 01:36:29,630
Bearing 0-5-9! 位置0-5-9

1073
01:36:29,760 --> 01:36:30,720
TORPEDO FIRED 鱼雷发射

1074
01:36:35,050 --> 01:36:38,220
Torpedo alert! Headed straight for us, 900 m! 鱼雷警报，冲我们来了，900米

1075
01:36:42,350 --> 01:36:43,400
Quiet. 安静

1076
01:36:43,690 --> 01:36:44,810
Quiet! 安静

1077
01:36:45,020 --> 01:36:45,940
We expected it. 早料到了

1078
01:36:46,320 --> 01:36:48,820
- We must break away. - It's what he wants. -我们得撤了 -他就想要我们……

1079
01:36:48,940 --> 01:36:50,570
To snap the wire. I stay put. 别切断引导线，我们待在原地

1080
01:36:51,650 --> 01:36:52,950
Maintain course. 保持航向

1081
01:36:53,780 --> 01:36:54,740
Go on, back off! 快撤吧

1082
01:36:54,870 --> 01:36:56,620
Snap your fucking wire! 切断你那该死的引导线

1083
01:36:56,740 --> 01:36:58,990
Captain, <i>Titan</i> is not breaking away. 船长，泰坦号不肯撤离

1084
01:36:59,540 --> 01:37:00,790
Torpedo, 700 m. 鱼雷，700米

1085
01:37:00,960 --> 01:37:02,670
- 700 m! - Accelerating on audio. -700米！ -音频加速了

1086
01:37:03,620 --> 01:37:05,500
Veer right. Dive! 右转，下潜

1087
01:37:06,670 --> 01:37:07,550
Chops! 通讯员

1088
01:37:08,000 --> 01:37:09,420
Veer right! Dive! 右转下潜！

1089
01:37:10,260 --> 01:37:11,590
Chops, what the hell! 通讯员，你干啥！

1090
01:37:13,090 --> 01:37:14,680
Break away. We're gonna die! 快撤，要死了

1091
01:37:14,800 --> 01:37:16,100
Don't let me down. 别搞砸了

1092
01:37:18,140 --> 01:37:19,060
Cut it out! 快切断它

1093
01:37:21,640 --> 01:37:23,560
We gotta break away! 我们得撤了

1094
01:37:24,730 --> 01:37:26,690
- We're gonna die! - Stay focused. -要死了！ -集中注意力

1095
01:37:29,070 --> 01:37:30,780
Focus on your screens! 盯着你们的屏幕

1096
01:37:38,370 --> 01:37:40,040
Captain, we're gonna catch it. 船长，就快击中我们了

1097
01:37:40,950 --> 01:37:41,830
Masks on! 带上面罩

1098
01:37:46,080 --> 01:37:47,290
<i>Hallowed be thy name</i> 上帝保佑

1099
01:37:48,130 --> 01:37:48,920
Masks on! 戴上面罩

1100
01:37:49,210 --> 01:37:51,920
<i>Your will be done on Earth as it is in Heaven</i> 死在地球宛若天堂

1101
01:37:52,380 --> 01:37:53,340
Men! 伙计们

1102
01:37:54,720 --> 01:37:56,300
It was an honour to sail with you. 和你们在一起我感到荣耀

1103
01:37:58,140 --> 01:37:59,510
We'll see this through! 自始至终

1104
01:38:01,020 --> 01:38:02,640
I'll take guidance on manual. 接下来由我人工引导

1105
01:38:03,140 --> 01:38:04,850
Bring up torpedo telemetry. 启动鱼雷遥测

1106
01:38:05,400 --> 01:38:07,360
Torpedo headed straight for target. 鱼雷直奔目标

1107
01:38:07,480 --> 01:38:08,980
Time to missile launch? 还有多久发射

1108
01:38:09,150 --> 01:38:10,070
40 seconds. 40秒

1109
01:38:10,730 --> 01:38:12,190
Buy ten more. 再争取10秒

1110
01:38:12,740 --> 01:38:13,610
Deploy decoy! 部署诱饵

1111
01:38:20,790 --> 01:38:21,490
FORMIDABLE 无畏号

1112
01:38:21,620 --> 01:38:23,000
Solution uncertain. Target moving. 轨迹改变，目标移动了

1113
01:38:23,540 --> 01:38:25,500
- No, that's a decoy. - Sure, sir? -不，那是诱饵 -确定吗，长官？

1114
01:38:25,620 --> 01:38:27,750
- Machine says no decoy. - Come left. -仪器没有现实诱饵 -向左

1115
01:38:27,880 --> 01:38:30,920
- I know. <i>Formidable</i>'s my baby. - Coming left. -我了解无畏号，就像我的孩子一样 -向左

1116
01:38:34,260 --> 01:38:36,630
Captain, torpedo headed straight for us. 船长，鱼雷直冲我们来了

1117
01:38:36,800 --> 01:38:39,010
Cut engines and sonar. We play dead. 切断发动机和声纳，我们装死

1118
01:38:43,560 --> 01:38:45,940
- It's gone! - Watch. It'll reappear there. -它不见了 -看好，它会重新出现在那里

1119
01:38:47,600 --> 01:38:48,770
Hold on. 等一下

1120
01:38:49,860 --> 01:38:50,570
Missile! 导弹！

1121
01:38:50,690 --> 01:38:52,320
Launch authorised in 20 secs! 授权发射还有20秒

1122
01:38:52,440 --> 01:38:53,900
Torpedo impact, 15 secs. 鱼雷还有15秒

1123
01:38:55,110 --> 01:38:56,110
It's over, sir. 完蛋了，长官

1124
01:38:59,070 --> 01:38:59,910
FORMIDABLE 无畏号

1125
01:39:00,030 --> 01:39:03,200
- Adopted! - On target, solution positive. -就这样 -看见目标了，方向正确

1126
01:39:03,740 --> 01:39:04,950
Target reached, 10 secs! 10秒命中目标

1127
01:39:07,160 --> 01:39:09,500
Blow air tanks. Create double target! 气舱排气，双重目标

1128
01:39:13,750 --> 01:39:15,470
Captain, launch authorised! 船长，可以发射了

1129
01:40:16,530 --> 01:40:17,820
Survivors? 有活的吗

1130
01:40:18,740 --> 01:40:19,780
Anyone? 有人吗？

1131
01:40:21,240 --> 01:40:22,280
Anyone answer me? 回答啊

1132
01:40:33,880 --> 01:40:34,790
Socks! 小鬼

1133
01:40:35,340 --> 01:40:36,590
C'mon, Socks! 来，小鬼

1134
01:40:54,610 --> 01:40:56,900
LAUNCH AUTHORISED 准备发射

1135
01:40:57,730 --> 01:41:00,360
<i>Control room, XO here. Do you copy?</i> 控制室，我是传令官，收到吗？

1136
01:41:03,780 --> 01:41:05,370
<i>Captain, do you copy?</i> 船长，听得到吗？

1137
01:41:07,080 --> 01:41:08,370
Control, do you copy? 控制室，收到吗

1138
01:41:10,370 --> 01:41:11,960
<i>Control, answer me!</i> 控制室，请回答

1139
01:41:14,580 --> 01:41:16,630
TUUM active. Sending distress message! TUUM激活，发送遇险信息

1140
01:41:16,920 --> 01:41:18,380
Negative, Chops. 不可以，通讯员

1141
01:41:19,130 --> 01:41:20,840
First, we launch the missile. 我们得先发射导弹

1142
01:41:23,470 --> 01:41:25,260
No air in circuit! 没有空气回路了

1143
01:41:25,430 --> 01:41:26,510
Masks off! 脱掉面罩

1144
01:41:26,680 --> 01:41:27,810
Monoxide. 一氧化碳

1145
01:41:28,640 --> 01:41:30,020
Air's contaminated, sir! 空气被污染了，长官

1146
01:41:30,180 --> 01:41:31,600
Evacuate control room. 疏散控制室

1147
01:41:31,770 --> 01:41:33,020
Evacuate! 疏散

1148
01:41:34,480 --> 01:41:35,610
Come on, captain. 快来，船长

1149
01:41:48,370 --> 01:41:50,290
Stay with me. We're going up. 跟着我，我们上去

1150
01:42:15,350 --> 01:42:16,480
<i>Captain...</i> 船长

1151
01:42:17,560 --> 01:42:19,320
<i>Captain, Chanteraide here.</i> 船长，我是尚特莱

1152
01:42:21,030 --> 01:42:22,400
<i>If you hear me...</i> 如果你能听到

1153
01:42:23,740 --> 01:42:25,360
<i>You always trusted me.</i> 你一直都相信我

1154
01:42:26,070 --> 01:42:27,450
<i>Trust me one last time.</i> 那么最后信我一次

1155
01:42:28,410 --> 01:42:30,740
I beg you, do not launch a missile. 我求你，别发射导弹

1156
01:42:31,620 --> 01:42:33,700
<i>It would be a grievous error.</i> 这是个严重的错误

1157
01:42:40,630 --> 01:42:42,840
<i>Most likely, these are my last words.</i> 也许，这是我最后的遗言

1158
01:42:46,130 --> 01:42:47,760
<i>I hear the wolf's call.</i> 我听见了狼嚎

1159
01:42:51,970 --> 01:42:53,390
Farewell, captain. 船长，永别了

1160
01:44:24,900 --> 01:44:25,860
Take it. 拿着

1161
01:44:27,530 --> 01:44:30,360
- You, admiral. - No, we'll get you out of here. -上将 -不，我们得把你弄出去

1162
01:44:33,780 --> 01:44:35,790
Socks, put it on. Now! 小鬼，穿上

1163
01:44:37,160 --> 01:44:40,120
Your ears will blow. Say goodbye to your eardrums. 你的耳朵会受压，和你的鼓膜说再见吧。

1164
01:44:49,300 --> 01:44:50,590
In there! 去那儿

1165
01:44:58,850 --> 01:44:59,810
Let's go! 走吧

1166
01:49:47,680 --> 01:49:53,440
THE WOLF'S CALL

1167
01:55:38,700 --> 01:55:40,990
Subtitles: Simon John

